{"lemma":"مُسَبِّبُو","slug":"مُسَبِّبُو","root":"س.ب.ب","root_slug":"س-ب-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ب-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18628","n18629"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90%D9%91%D8%A8%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cause"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instigator"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of سَبَّبَ (sabbaba, “to cause”)."},"ipa":["/mu.sab.bib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18628","headword_ar":"مُسَبَّبٌ","root":"sb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much reviled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see its verb]. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musab~abapN","text_ar":"مُسَبَّبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an epithet applied to camels, (S, K, TA,) or to horses, (A,) and to wild asses, (TA,) means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Goodly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * K, TA:) because (S, TA) they are such that one says of them, (S, A, TA,) when admiring them, (S, TA,) or when deeming them goodly, or excellent, (A,) May God curse them, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAtalahaA A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"قَاتَلَهَا ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, A, TA,) and abase them: ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axozaAhaA","text_ar":"اَخْزَاهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": A, TA:) how goodly, or excellent, are they! (TA.)       -A2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Made, appointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, as a means,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cause, of attainment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplishment,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^amorK","text_ar":"لِاَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Caused,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occasioned:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing caused"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occasioned; an effect."},{"kind":"text","text":"] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA musab~abN Eano h`*aA","text_ar":"هٰذَا مُسَبَّبٌ عَنْ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is caused,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occasioned, by that: this is an effect of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arising from, that"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n18629","headword_ar":"مُسَبِّبٌ","root":"sb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Reviling much:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see its verb.       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Making, appointing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preparing, a means,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cause:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occasioning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a causer"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musab~ibu AlA^asobaAbi","text_ar":"مُسَبِّبُ الاَسْبَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Appointer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Preparer, of means"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Causer of cau